    "description": "Lumora is a cutting-edge DeFi protocol that redefines lending by integrating an Automated Market Maker (AMM) with a dynamic Loan-to-Value (LTV) model. It leverages Sonic Blockchain, Chainlink CCIP, and Uniswap for cross-chain functionality and robust risk management.",
    "keywords": [
        "blockchain",
        "smart-contracts",
        "defi",
        "sonic",
        "chainlink",
        "uniswap",
        "amm",
        "ltv"
    ],
